{"type":"message","id":"dc36d9d8","parentId":"7ca20b72","timestamp":"2026-05-13T07:56:02.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is telling me I can use a \"searxng\" skill if needed. Let me check if such a skill exists in the available skills list... \n\nLooking at the available skills listed in my system prompt, I don't see a \"searxng\" skill. The user might be referring to a skill they want me to use or one that exists elsewhere. \n\nSince they're telling me I can use it, they might be setting up or mentioning a search-related skill. Let me check if there's a searxng skill available, or if they're giving me permission to use web search tools.\n\nActually, I do have web_search and web_fetch tools available. The user seems to be giving me permission to use searxng for searching. But I don't see it in my available skills list.\n\nMaybe they're saying that if I need to search, I can use searxng - perhaps they've configured it somewhere or are telling me it's available. I should acknowledge this and let them know I've noted it, or ask if they want me to look into setting it up.\n\nLet me just acknowledge this briefly since it's just a casual message about a skill being available.","thinkingSignature":"91536cc0a440c167b71e7ef9a93607ae12e4066a864e90ff4c7fdeabe8908560"},{"type":"text","text":"收到，我已经注意到 searxng 这个工具。如果需要进行网络搜索，我会用的。需要我做什么吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":261,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":17755,"totalTokens":18163,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778658950745,"responseId":"06536187dc2993235a923b5e08392b49"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f753016","parentId":"dc36d9d8","timestamp":"2026-05-13T07:57:45.122Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f76a1e620bcc34e3e44153be57]\nou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd: 作为我的电商团队总监，需要你整合一套可以执行的完整的打法，针对tiktokshop 东南亚的 打法。 我经营半年有点撑不住了。 如何能让你完整的了解到当前店铺的情况呢，"}],"timestamp":1778659065121}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6f76a1e620bcc34e3e44153be57\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-13 15:57 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"f0dca827","parentId":"3f753016","timestamp":"2026-05-13T07:57:45.122Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"bf1715c8","parentId":"f0dca827","timestamp":"2026-05-13T07:58:04.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问如何让我完整了解到当前店铺的情况，作为TikTok Shop东南亚的电商团队总监，需要整合一套可执行的完整打法。\n\n这是一个需要深入了解业务现状的问题。我需要先了解：\n1. 店铺的基本数据（GMV、订单量、客单价等）\n2. 运营现状（类目、SKU、粉丝数、直播情况等）\n3. 市场竞争情况\n4. 团队配置\n\n用户说经营半年有点撑不住了，说明可能面临亏损或资金压力。\n\n我应该给用户一个清晰的\"信息收集清单\"，让他知道需要提供什么资料，我才能给出针对性的打法。\n\n同时我也可以主动搜索一些TikTok Shop东南亚的最新市场情况和打法策略。\n\n让我先搜索一下TikTok Shop东南亚的最新动态和打法思路，这样可以给用户一个更专业的开场。","thinkingSignature":"d4bdbf4e0280f8ef6fe94777ec837cb7171bbe018733d83525e8237dc9068dd6"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，半年确实不容易。先说个判断——**能撑6个月，说明产品和供应链有一定基础，问题多半出在流量效率和运营节奏上**。\n\n要给出有针对性的完整打法，我需要先了解你的真实情况。咱们分两步走：\n\n---\n\n## 第一步：你需要给我哪些信息？\n\n**📊 核心数据（尽量给，越全越好）**\n| 维度 | 举例 |\n|------|------|\n| 销售额 | 近3个月GMV、月环比、客单价 |\n| 类目/品 | 在做什么类目？主要爆款是什么？ |\n| 站点 | 东南亚哪个国家？泰国/印尼/越南/马来/菲律宾？ |\n| 团队配置 | 有多少人？主播、运营、投放各几个？ |\n| 账号情况 | 粉丝数、直播频次、场均观看 |\n| 投放情况 | 付费投了多少钱？ROI多少？ |\n| 物流/仓储 | 自有还是云仓？时效和成本？ |\n| 资金状况 | 月亏多少？还能撑多久？ |\n\n**📁 能提供截图就更好**\n- 店铺后台数据截图\n- 投放报表\n- 直播数据\n\n---\n\n## 第二步：我同步准备东南亚TikTok Shop打法框架\n\n我先去搜一下最新的东南亚TikTok Shop市场动态和头部玩家的打法策略，结合我的电商经验，给你整理一套**经过验证的可执行方案**。\n\n---\n\n你先把这些信息发给我，我结合你的实际情况来调整打法，而不是给你一套通用废话。\n\n**现在最紧急的是哪个问题？** 流量、转化、还是资金链？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":491,"cacheRead":17503,"cacheWrite":370,"totalTokens":18511,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778659065122,"responseId":"065361f90a3d9817289633d21b5d050a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac413d17","parentId":"bf1715c8","timestamp":"2026-05-13T08:12:51.017Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[message_id: om_x100b6f77692cb0e4c2d5688529b790f]\nou_8095cb7e32537c4c52f38d13cc0f28dd: 哎，另外的话，我还得给你配置一些工具啊。嗯，当前的这个系统是乌班图二二是在桌面的上面也有浏览器，你可以用默认的C，DP去控制浏览器，单起一个独立的实力来去访问后台，我可以提供一个权限。那总之就是我们现在要尽快去跑通。那你知道现在咱们的团队有多少个角色吗"}],"timestamp":1778659971016}}
