{"type":"message","id":"8e12a03c","parentId":"849d97a7","timestamp":"2026-05-13T08:13:07.401Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about team roles, and they also mentioned setting up browser access (CDP) to access their TikTok Shop backend directly. They seem to be in a hurry to get this running.\n\nLet me think about what they've shared:\n1. They want to configure CDP browser access for me to directly access their TikTok Shop dashboard\n2. They asked if I know how many team roles they have\n3. They're saying they need to configure some tools for me\n\nI should be honest - I don't know their team composition because they haven't told me yet. I should:\n1. Ask about the team roles since they seem to want to share that info\n2. Acknowledge the browser/CDP setup - this is interesting, they're offering to give me direct access to their shop backend\n\nLet me respond directly and ask about the team while acknowledging the browser setup suggestion.","thinkingSignature":"bedf99a254a6df7aa527961bc1bb44fcf98b6f67272295f4634b02a3d3719fa6"},{"type":"text","text":"我目前不知道咱们的团队有多少人、什么角色——这个信息你还没告诉我。\n\n关于浏览器控制访问后台，这个思路很好。CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol) 可以让我直接操控浏览器进入系统，效率会高很多。\n\n**现在告诉我：**\n1. 团队有多少人，各自什么角色？\n2. 给我开个账号权限，怎么连接？\n\n你要是愿意，直接给我开一个子账号+密码，我用浏览器帮你跑后台数据，比截图更快更完整。\n\n**先把团队情况说一下？** 几个人、谁负责什么——我需要知道这张牌桌上有几张牌，才能帮你规划打法。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":305,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":18328,"totalTokens":18780,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778659971018,"responseId":"06536583d53cdcce3d96d2cd31e56b39"}}
