{"type":"message","id":"e070a710","parentId":"76ac2944","timestamp":"2026-05-13T08:13:35.097Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在说\"在系统创建的这些Agent当中，你们应我来想办法\"——意思是让我看看当前系统里已经有哪些Agent/角色，让我从这些现有的Agent中想办法。\n\n我应该先查看一下当前有哪些可用的Agent。我可以用 agents_list 来看看，或者用 sessions_list 来看看当前系统里有哪些会话/agent。\n\n让我先列出当前可用的agents。","thinkingSignature":"da73de2483eb4d5d2a83ac16603f0afea57e02f09a7c56665931a2d277bcda96"},{"type":"text","text":"\n明白了，让我先看看当前系统里有哪些可用的Agent/角色。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ipza73coxjwj_1","name":"agents_list","arguments":{}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ipza73coxjwj_2","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"includeDerivedTitles":true,"includeLastMessage":true}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":147,"cacheRead":18077,"cacheWrite":445,"totalTokens":18816,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778660009902,"responseId":"065365aa7c301cf443d5ab2699403b5a"}}
